Structure of the DIVA project:
=======================================
Folder          	Contains
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
documentation 		manual for the DIVA and printout of help. 
Examples		example files that you may try to test your installation
Src			source code of the project. 

Compilation:
=======================================
To compile the project type the following in your terminal (you need a C compiler installed on your system):
>cd ./src
>make
As the result of compilation you should obtain ‘diva’ executable  which you should be able to run by typing:
>./diva

